# Shared build-context ignore for both backend/Dockerfile and frontend/Dockerfile
# (both build from the monorepo root). Do NOT exclude frontend/ here: the web
# image does `COPY frontend frontend`. The backend image only copies backend/
# and packages/, so leaving frontend/ in its context is harmless.
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/.next
**/build
**/.dart_tool
mobile/
resources/
scripts/
*.md
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!backend/.env.production.example
